<h4> Where is child abuse most common?</h4>
<p> Child abuse is most common in high-income countries. The most common form of child abuse is psychological abuse. </p>

<h4> Is the abuse my fault?</h4>
<p> NO. The abuse is never your fault and you should never blame yourself. It is your abuser's fault that you get hurt. </p>



